---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Work">
    <section class="section">
        <h2>Work</h2>
        <p class="lead">
        Recent projects focused on streamlining operations, building data systems, 
        and automating workflows.
        </p>
    </section>

    <div class="projects">
        <article class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
            <h3>Warehouse inventory system</h3>
            <div class="project-meta">
            <span>2024</span>
            <span>•</span>
            <span>Operations</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-content">
            <p>
            Rebuilt tracking system from spreadsheets to database. Eliminated manual data 
            entry, added real-time sync, reduced processing time by 68%. Team saved 10 hours 
            weekly on administrative tasks.
            </p>
            <div class="project-details">
            <h4>Challenge</h4>
            <p>
                Warehouse team maintaining 15 Excel spreadsheets manually. Data entry took 
                2+ hours daily. Version conflicts and errors caused shipment delays.
            </p>
            
            <h4>Approach</h4>
            <p>
                Mapped existing workflow, identified bottlenecks. Built PostgreSQL database 
                with real-time sync. Created simple interface for data entry with validation. 
                Automated common tasks.
            </p>
            
            <h4>Outcome</h4>
            <p>
                Processing time reduced from 3 hours to 20 minutes. Zero version conflicts. 
                Team can focus on actual warehouse operations instead of spreadsheet maintenance.
            </p>
            
            <div class="tech-stack">
                <span>Python</span>
                <span>PostgreSQL</span>
                <span>Pandas</span>
                <span>Automation</span>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
            <h3>Operations dashboard</h3>
            <div class="project-meta">
            <span>2024</span>
            <span>•</span>
            <span>Data pipeline</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-content">
            <p>
            Built ETL pipeline processing 80k+ transactions daily. Created real-time dashboard 
            for operational metrics. Reduced status meetings from daily to weekly as team 
            could self-serve data.
            </p>
            <div class="project-details">
            <h4>Challenge</h4>
            <p>
                Operations team had no visibility into real-time metrics. Data scattered across 
                5 systems. Daily status meetings required to understand current state.
            </p>
            
            <h4>Approach</h4>
            <p>
                Built ETL pipeline connecting all data sources. Created unified data model. 
                Designed dashboard showing key metrics updated every 5 minutes. Made it fast 
                and reliable.
            </p>
            
            <h4>Outcome</h4>
            <p>
                Team has real-time visibility. Status meetings reduced from 1 hour daily to 
                30 minutes weekly. Faster response to operational issues. Data-driven decisions.
            </p>
            
            <div class="tech-stack">
                <span>Airflow</span>
                <span>BigQuery</span>
                <span>dbt</span>
                <span>React</span>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
            <h3>System integration</h3>
            <div class="project-meta">
            <span>2023</span>
            <span>•</span>
            <span>Integration</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-content">
            <p>
            Connected 5 legacy systems through custom adapters. Handled data transformation, 
            built unified data model. Operations team gained single source of truth for 
            cross-system reporting.
            </p>
            <div class="project-details">
            <h4>Challenge</h4>
            <p>
                Five different systems (CRM, inventory, accounting, fulfillment, support) 
                not talking to each other. Manual data reconciliation taking hours weekly. 
                No unified view of operations.
            </p>
            
            <h4>Approach</h4>
            <p>
                Built custom adapters for each system's API. Created unified data model 
                mapping concepts across systems. Handled data transformation and validation. 
                Set up automated sync.
            </p>
            
            <h4>Outcome</h4>
            <p>
                Single source of truth for operational data. Automated daily sync. Cross-system 
                reporting now possible. Team saved 10+ hours weekly on manual reconciliation.
            </p>
            
            <div class="tech-stack">
                <span>Python</span>
                <span>REST APIs</span>
                <span>Docker</span>
                <span>Data modeling</span>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </article>
    </div>

    <footer class="work-footer">
        <p>
        Interested in similar projects? <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
        </p>
    </footer>
</Layout>

    <style>
    .section {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
        padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    
    .lead {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    .projects {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-xl);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    }
    
    .project {
        padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    
    .project:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .project-header {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }
    
    .project-header h3 {
        margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm) 0;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .project-meta {
        font-family: var(--font-heading);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--space-sm);
    }
    
    .project-content > p {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }
    
    .project-details {
        background: var(--color-surface);
        padding: var(--space-lg);
        border-left: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    
    .project-details h4 {
        font-family: var(--font-heading);
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: var(--space-lg);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    }
    
    .project-details h4:first-child {
        margin-top: 0;
    }
    
    .project-details p {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }
    
    .tech-stack {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: var(--space-sm);
        margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    }
    
    .tech-stack span {
        font-family: var(--font-heading);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        background: var(--color-bg);
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        border-radius: 3px;
    }
    
    .work-footer {
        padding-top: var(--space-lg);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .work-footer p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }
</style>